{"tid":843479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"助低收入學生面試　紐約公共圖書館免費借領呔公事包","createTime":"2018-10-01T07:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T09:04:41.000Z","uid":19552,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"24b75dc742b36ac9aee8aa8d221f98233187a18e","tid":843479,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"所謂「人靠衣裝」，整潔的外表能夠給人好印象，合適的打扮對於工作面試更為重要。美國紐約一個公共圖書館最近提供貼心服務，向收入有限的學生借出面試所需的領呔及公事包，以減輕他們的負擔，協助他們踏進職場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1882773/org/d78caa8e2597e0bebc4a2209c184b3da.jpg/YQ-jAQVeSTLQ9SJes9RsUuscxEqGPdVH_qqLxP6qi8Q?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1882773%2Forg%2Fd78caa8e2597e0bebc4a2209c184b3da.jpg%2FYQ-jAQVeSTLQ9SJes9RsUuscxEqGPdVH_qqLxP6qi8Q%3Fv%3Dw800&h=b2e7f988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1882793/org/da1cd61b90f1037e80e800d81e1ca0af.jpg/dDuIFU2wEcWSRrWGaHikuJ9NqXLG6_Sf7A5gf-wOYH8?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1882793%2Forg%2Fda1cd61b90f1037e80e800d81e1ca0af.jpg%2FdDuIFU2wEcWSRrWGaHikuJ9NqXLG6_Sf7A5gf-wOYH8%3Fv%3Dw480&h=97144b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於不少學生來說，西裝、公事包等物品只在畢業禮或工作面試時才會用到，使用頻率雖然低，卻要花費大筆金錢購買，紐約河濱圖書館（Riverside Library）的職員Michelle去年協助學生準備大學面試和兼職工作時留意到這情況，靈機一動想到一項創新服務－為有需要的學生提供面試所需的服裝，「很多青少年參加我舉辦的求職講座時都表示不知道面試時應該穿什麼衣服，或者根本沒有正裝」。<br />\n<br />\nMichelle將念頭全寫進計劃書，提交至紐約公共圖書館的創新計劃；該計劃每年會選出25項由圖書館工作人員提出的項目，提供資源加以實行，目的是以教育或以其他方式使圖書館所在的社區受益。Michelle的計劃書最終成功從超過300項參選提案中脫穎而出，「工作服裝圖書館」（Grow Up Work Fashion Library）應運而生。"},{"pid":"be9bd19b36ae17781ad1e8f403a4a0ee40bcfc88","tid":843479,"uid":26506,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:42:45.000Z","msg":"香港嘅話要借床位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0928dd5bef86bce66aa6223e6aa04803b17a78","tid":843479,"uid":132587,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"如果香港中央圖書館既話<br />\n條呔會唔會好大陣口水味 借個公事包對住佢自言自語<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b403b43b0425a253d5499be23059193cf66065","tid":843479,"uid":126554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"見完工成功左都要買架啦 遲早既事"},{"pid":"703450df75cba86f7bb341dee10f358eb97ea32d","tid":843479,"uid":64345,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"91b403b43b0425a253d5499be23059193cf66065","tid":843479,"uid":126554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"見完工成功左都要買架啦 遲早既事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:54:30.000Z","msg":"圖書館都無諗過佢地會成功"},{"pid":"a4b22d13cd02d6ff77683ec644c569ebd1cda07c","tid":843479,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:55:26.000Z","msg":"應該要借埋衫俾佢地返工用<br />\n直至到咗第一個月糧有錢買衫為止"},{"pid":"22dbe113d87290ca6ad08449197d08103058268c","tid":843479,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4b22d13cd02d6ff77683ec644c569ebd1cda07c","tid":843479,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:55:26.000Z","msg":"應該要借埋衫俾佢地返工用<br />\n直至到咗第一個月糧有錢買衫為止"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:56:06.000Z","msg":"應該要借埋衫俾佢地返工用<br />\n直至出咗第一個月糧有錢買衫為止"},{"pid":"a71d7497cfacd721791cdac163c86b6e7ec61619","tid":843479,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22dbe113d87290ca6ad08449197d08103058268c","tid":843479,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4b22d13cd02d6ff77683ec644c569ebd1cda07c","tid":843479,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:55:26.000Z","msg":"應該要借埋衫俾佢地返工用<br />\n直至到咗第一個月糧有錢買衫為止"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:56:06.000Z","msg":"應該要借埋衫俾佢地返工用<br />\n直至出咗第一個月糧有錢買衫為止"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T08:03:56.000Z","msg":"應該借埋第一個月糧<br />\n直至出左第二個月糧為止"},{"pid":"3521a1cb49e495b2f1439dd7a79744ce00c